I wanted this to be a good show, i wanted it to be good Star Trek and a love letter to Captain Picard's character and morals.  

//edit: after 10 episodes, the verdict remains unchanged, this is not worthy of Star Trek, it is the exact opposite of what i would have wanted to happen to my Childhood Heroes.
